Package com.github.tadukoo.util.fileformat

Class TadFormatNodeHeader

java.lang.Object
com.github.tadukoo.util.fileformat.TadFormatNodeHeader
public class TadFormatNodeHeader
extends java.lang.Object
This class defines the Tad Format Node Header section that should be at the top of all files.
